The paper proposes a lossy image compression system using deep learning techniques, specifically an autoencoder structure. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of importance maps and bitrate control, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also mentions the use of quantizers, which are related to information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.MM, followed by cs.LG, cs.IR, and cs.IT.
